short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Shiba Inu wallpaper turn new tab to custom HD Shiba Inu dog background. Cute Shiba Inu wallpaper theme for dogs fans.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extension Features:

1. Automatically shuffle your Shiba Inu wallpaper with every new tab.
2. Choose a random Shiba Inu background or pin your favorites in the wallpaper selection panel.
3. Integrated Google search bar.
4. Direct links to your email and social media profiles.
5. Display the current date and time automatically.
6. New note feature for jotting down tasks.
7. Quick links to your most frequently visited websites.
8. Simplified access to your bookmarks.
9. Shortcut panel for adding and accessing websites quickly.
10. Instant access to Google applications.
11. Direct link to explore more themes.
12. Effortless sharing options to social media.
13. Convenient download options for wallpapers.
14. Quick launch feature for playing games.
15. Activate entertaining animations like snow, rain, falling leaves, and fireworks on your Shiba Inu new tab.
